[Ivan clears throat]

31:01.191 --> 31:02.192
[knocking]

31:04.929 --> 31:06.264
- [Ivan] Hey.
- Hey. Come on.

31:09.333 --> 31:11.299
- Gentlemen.
- Ivan!

31:11.301 --> 31:13.367
- Come on in.
- Jesus.

31:13.369 --> 31:15.202
