31:58.214 --> 31:59.981
Nah, I'm just fuckin' with ya.

31:59.983 --> 32:02.217
Believe me, you're gonna get
all your money.

32:02.219 --> 32:04.151
[snickers]

32:04.153 --> 32:06.988
Pay attention. I have something
else for you. Another job,

32:06.990 --> 32:09.024
kind of special.

32:09.026 --> 32:12.661
