43:54.197 --> 43:55.365
[buzzing continues]

43:57.233 --> 43:58.865
[Ivan clears throat]

43:58.867 --> 44:00.371
- Hello.
- Hi.

44:01.804 --> 44:02.873
[Elyse] <i>It's Elyse.</i>

44:03.806 --> 44:06.042
Uh, hey.

44:07.143 --> 44:08.144
[Ivan] <i>Uh...</i>

44:09.079 --> 44:10.378
Can I come up?

44:10.380 --> 44:13.384
Uh, of course. Yeah, uh, yup.

44:14.416 --> 44:16.152
Fuck. Shit.

44:17.753 --> 44:19.119
[Ivan] <i>Yeah, I'm buzzing you.</i>

44:19.121 --> 44:20.755
[door buzzing]

44:20.757 --> 44:21.889
Fuck, fuck, fuck.

44:21.891 --> 44:22.893
Fuck, fuck, fuck.

44:24.927 --> 44:25.929
[light thudding]

44:29.331 --> 44:31.965
- Hi.
- [Elyse] Hi.

44:31.967 --> 44:34.034
I, um,
I scratched on my eight ball.

44:34.036 --> 44:35.302
Ah. You did.

44:35.304 --> 44:36.938
I thought
we could talk about it.

44:36.940 --> 44:40.407
Sure, we can talk about it.
Yeah, um, how did you...

44:40.409 --> 44:42.744
- How did you find me?
- Oh, um...

44:42.746 --> 44:44.445
I, uh, looked in
your wallet that night.

44:44.447 --> 44:48.148
Oh, okay, nice. Shit, um...

44:48.150 --> 44:51.251
Rematch? Down the street,
great bar, great table.

44:51.253 --> 44:52.787
- Sure, yeah.
- [Ivan] Great. Okay.

44:52.789 --> 44:54.287
- Okay.
- [Ivan] Just give me one second.

44:54.289 --> 44:55.356
Stay right there.

44:55.358 --> 44:57.161
