45:09.806 --> 45:10.871
- [Elyse] Mm.
- Ready to go?

45:10.873 --> 45:12.442
- [Elyse] Yeah.
- [Ivan] Okay.

45:15.277 --> 45:16.376
So,

45:16.378 --> 45:19.847
something I was thinking about
this, uh, Aton guy,

45:19.849 --> 45:21.449
you know, the dickhead producer.

45:21.451 --> 45:22.450
Yup.

45:22.452 --> 45:24.985
