45:31.193 --> 45:33.327
[Elyse]
<i>I, um, I did something dumb.</i>

45:33.329 --> 45:35.362
<i>Probably out of shame or spite.</i>

45:35.364 --> 45:36.930
<i>I stole
the sweetest little necklace</i>

45:36.932 --> 45:38.999
<i>off of Mrs. Eisenstadt's vanity.</i>

45:39.001 --> 45:40.400
[Ivan] Hmm.

45:40.402 --> 45:43.470
