45:43.472 --> 45:44.738
[Elyse]
<i>I don't think married women</i>

45:44.740 --> 45:47.407
<i>like finding other girls'
panties in their hamper.</i>

45:47.409 --> 45:51.211
<i>Anyway, um, it turned out to be
