46:00.123 --> 46:02.123
<i>and I owe him $250,000.</i>

46:02.125 --> 46:04.825
<i>And when I said, "Or what?"
he said,</i>

46:04.827 --> 46:07.161
<i>"You'll never work
in this town again, kid."</i>

46:07.163 --> 46:09.496
