trying to do.

46:22.378 --> 46:24.979
One Italian horror movie
at a time.

46:24.981 --> 46:28.249
I, um, I still owe him $200,000,

46:28.251 --> 46:32.186
or as he likes to say,
"400 million lira."

46:32.188 --> 46:33.521
