to have that

46:33.523 --> 46:34.988
lying around, do you?

46:34.990 --> 46:36.293
Not in lira, no.

46:39.862 --> 46:42.028
That was a good game.
You win fair and square.

46:42.030 --> 46:43.898
No, no. Keep it. We're even.

46:43.900 --> 46:45.066
- [Elyse] Hm.
- Um,

46:45.068 --> 46:47.400
there is one thing, though,
and you know, hear me out.

46:47.402 --> 46:50.304
This may sound
a little crazy, but...

46:50.306 --> 46:55.175
would you be interested
in helping me out, uh...

46:55.177 --> 46:57.478
you know, returning
the fake boyfriend favor?

46:57.480 --> 46:59.045
- How so?
- [Ivan] Well,

46:59.047 --> 47:00.514
you're an actress, right?

47:00.516 --> 47:01.715
- Sure.
- Well,

47:01.717 --> 47:05.519
would you be interested in
becoming a potential home buyer

47:05.521 --> 47:07.153
in the greater Costa Mesa area?

47:07.155 --> 47:08.222
[Elyse] Absolutely not,

47:08.224 --> 47:09.557
but it sounds like
that's the part.

47:09.559 --> 47:11.191
Yeah, that's the part.

47:11.193 --> 47:13.163
I feel like there's something
you're not telling me.

47:15.297 --> 47:16.299
Maybe.

47:19.202 --> 47:22.068
What's, um, in the house?

47:22.070 --> 47:23.170
[Ivan] Now, I gotta figure out

47:23.172 --> 47:24.405
if there's something
in there or not.

47:24.407 --> 47:25.409
[Elyse] Hm.

47:27.409 --> 47:28.976
When?

47:28.978 --> 47:30.577
Next weekend.

47:30.579 --> 47:32.382
