01:18:33.140 --> 01:18:35.143
[foreboding music]

01:18:56.564 --> 01:18:59.067
[Elyse] No, of course not.
That's fine.

01:19:00.033 --> 01:19:01.168
Yeah, you too.

01:19:02.369 --> 01:19:03.471
Piece of shit.

01:19:05.139 --> 01:19:07.039
[Dimitri] You all right?

01:19:07.041 --> 01:19:08.440
