[scoffs]
He stood me up.

01:19:11.878 --> 01:19:14.412
Such a prick. He sends a car
for me in Laguna Beach,

01:19:14.414 --> 01:19:16.581
- and then he doesn't show.
- [phone rings]

01:19:16.583 --> 01:19:18.487
I'm so sick of this shit.
[chuckles]

